---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout title="Now — nbdevlab" description="What I am experimenting with at the moment.">
  <section aria-labelledby="now-title">
    <h1 id="now-title">Now</h1>
    <p>This is what’s currently running through the nbdevlab brain, updated whenever the calendar reminders nag me.</p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="focus-title" class="mt-10">
    <h2 id="focus-title">Active focus areas</h2>
    <ul class="now-list">
      <li>
        <h3>Edge automation</h3>
        <p>Refining Cloudflare Workers that cache GitHub activity, sync Decap CMS content, and hydrate dashboards in milliseconds.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Homelab resilience</h3>
        <p>Testing UPS failover drills, updating ZFS snapshots, and verifying incident runbooks stay accurate.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>OpenAI Codex exploration</h3>
        <p>Pairing Codex with CLI automation to scaffold repeatable notebook-to-worker pipelines.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="reading-title" class="mt-12">
    <h2 id="reading-title">Reading &amp; listening</h2>
    <ul class="now-list">
      <li>
        <h3>Book</h3>
        <p>Re-reading "Building Microservices" by Sam Newman to refresh observability patterns.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Podcast</h3>
        <p>Stack Overflow Podcast — episodes on edge deployment stories and AI pairing.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Newsletter</h3>
        <p>Last Week in AWS to keep tabs on interesting managed service launches that can complement Cloudflare.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <style>
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 2.5vw + 1rem, 3.1rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      max-width: 65ch;
    }
    .now-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .now-list h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .now-list p {
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</SiteLayout>
